STEPS:

1) Connect remote.control.box & rover (pi) to local wifi network.
2) Start reverse tunnel ssh from rover
3) ssh into tunnel
4) start python camera control
5) start server servo control

REVERSE TUNNEL FOR ROVER

FROM rover:
#sets up reverse tunnel
ssh -X -R 19992:localhost:22 root@remote.control.box


FROM remote.control.box
ssh pi@localhost -p 19992